		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T2D</code>: Deployment</h1>
		Deployment + Portability. Work about putting languages into use across environments: deployment pipelines, portability across platforms, packaging, distribution, integration into build systems, IDEs or CI/CD, operational concerns such as language servers in toolchains. If the key novelty is compilation/code generation, we may prefer <a href="t4c.html">T4C</a>.
